  <text id="BadLuckProtection_DescBonusCalculationMode"
    >Normalized: All abnormalities gain bonus at the same rate. The bonus is based on how many PE boxes you filled out of the total.
Example: filling 5 out of 10 PE boxes counts as 0.5.

Per PE-Box: Abnormalities with more PE boxes gain bonus faster. Each filled PE box adds 1 to the bonus.
Example: filling 7 PE boxes counts as 7.</text
